protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing buildings (Class B1(c) & B8) and the erection of a part 4, part 5, part 6 and part 7 storey building comprising 1,219 sqm of commercial  floorspace (Use Class B1) at basement and ground floor levels and 76 residential units (28 x 1-bed; 35 x 2-bed and 13 x 3-bed) (Class C3) including disabled car parking, landscaped courtyard and communal amenity areas.
